{"tid":1214643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尋日野餐好dry，想煮野食","createTime":"2019-06-13T04:54:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T05:34:43.000Z","uid":5939,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f5260799fde3eef27bb40d99382882c0a026ba98","tid":1214643,"uid":5939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:54:45.000Z","msg":"有無人覺得尋日野餐食d野好dry<br />\n我決定左下次野餐要煮野食<br />\n簡單d來講，我會帶兩個煎pan,幾隻雞蛋，同大量嘅油<br />\n1) 煎pan: 1個煎pan係唔夠，萬一煮到著曬火，你用水淋熄佢，<span style=\"color: red;\">產生大量煙霧</span>，無辦法只好用另一個煎pan滅煙，當然，你帶鑊都無問題:仲有就係野外難免都有d野狗搶食，呢個時侯可以用煎pan來做武器，趕走d野狗<br />\n2) 雞蛋 : 帶雞蛋當然為左煎蛋，仲有比d野狗騷擾個時可以掟走佢<br />\n3) 大量油: 為左令d食身無禁dry,絕對唔係為左搞事<br />\n火種方面，其實用吉野家邊爐都夠煎蛋，你帶發電機用電磁爐煮野食都ok<br />\n唔知大家有無其他方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f286ec3d609a6fda768410ae458ac198bf6d5b8a","tid":1214643,"uid":5939,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:56:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"48800c867a3fd37c3bca5a99a56b82c95ada3ac6","tid":1214643,"uid":5939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:58:26.000Z","msg":"無人煮食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50446f1acee933fb2c8cc84fc6e233b74810178b","tid":1214643,"uid":5939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:00:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e303171d740ba40ddd0b40b6dedeaa95b15bed","tid":1214643,"uid":5939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:03:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1d6b2d81a7510603a3ca4168cff38280b3fe25c9","tid":1214643,"uid":5939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:06:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"012915f01acd847bbff3ad892885685bc760fb8f","tid":1214643,"uid":76330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:13:26.000Z","msg":"發電機有難度，佢唔再好似五年前咁畀我地慢慢玩，家陣日日清，要有充足既logistic support, 但一入中心位置少少就要用步兵，發電機會唔會太大？<br />\n雞蛋唔錯，天氣熱，考慮下雪冰整凍飲？"},{"pid":"d9e449429698160a66b2df4238c41b1ab4b7f13c","tid":1214643,"uid":5939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:14:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>發電機有難度，佢唔再好似五年前咁畀我地慢慢玩，家陣日日清，要有充足既logistic support, 但一入中心位置少少就要用步兵，發電機會唔會太大？<br />\n雞蛋唔錯，天氣熱，考慮下雪冰整凍飲？</blockquote><br />\n所以麻算囉 最重要唔係火 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdb684816c92f37f182b9bcec1bafe3da0b8d4a1","tid":1214643,"uid":5939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:18:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f2fb62164b884e04cd1bda1e09cd8e39d5910e10","tid":1214643,"uid":104086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:20:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dd898a83c7c387f11693e85a854c358bdd487e5","tid":1214643,"uid":5939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:27:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1e39b5f1a514af688f7a1724a9229da2973dd733","tid":1214643,"uid":5939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:34:43.000Z","msg":"push"}]}